description: While some commentators are relieved, others fear Europe has been weakened.
title: Brexit: European press asks 'was it worth it?'
title_page: Brexit: European press asks 'was it worth it?' - BBC News
maintext: "Things will get worse before they get better," the Italian financial daily Il Sole 24 Ore says. It adds that the New Year will test the British "concept that whatever we lose by leaving the EU we gain in commercial deals with the rest of the world".
